44-3320.Legal service insurance corporation; laws applicable.

All corporations organized under sections 44-3312 and 44-3313 shall be governed by such other laws regulating the business of insurance and profit and nonprofit corporations as do not conflict with sections 44-3301 to 44-3327.

SourceLaws 1979, LB 52, ยง 20.
